data.description: Incredible investment opportunity in South St. Louis City!  Check out this large 3BR/1.5BA, ALL brick, corner lot home on a quiet street.  Features include newer roof, plumbing, remodeled main floor full bath, 8 car parking pad, wheelchair ramp, handicap accessible doors and additional lot (3840 Ohio).  Add egressed windows so that you can utilize the additional rooms in the basement as 4th and 5th bedrooms and collect higher rent.  Start making money on Day 1!  Section 8 tenant currently pays $1,030/month with plenty of room to increase rent.  Start building your investment portfolio today!  Minutes away from downtown St. Louis, parks, shopping and public transportation.  No showings without an accepted contract.  Sold as is. please use Special Sales Contract.***DO NOT DISTURB TENANT***
